The Telegraph - Calcutta : Metro

 Good Morning

 Hello It's Sunday, June 10, 2007

 Movie Magic

 Attend a special screening of Shrek 3 , presented by The Telegraph and Advertising Club Calcutta at Priya cinema, 9.30 am. Show open to Advertising Club members and guests.

 Career Fair

 Be there at a career fair organised by St Xaviers College, in association with The Telegraph, at the college auditorium, 11am.

 Music moves 

 Participate in a tabla workshop with Sujit Saha, at Gandhi Colony Boys School, 8am to 8pm.

 Stagecraft

 Watch plays at Greenwood Spirit Theatre Festival at Tapan Theatre. Today: Bite by Compass, 3pm, and Hai Ram by Songlap, 6pm.

 Eye on Art

 Walk through Visual World of Women Artists , an exhibition of paintings and drawings, at Samokal Art Gallery, 4pm to 8pm. 

 See Khela, works on paper and canvas by Arunima Choudhury, at Seagull Arts and Media Resource Centre, 2pm to 8pm. 




